thread.title_full: My Passport Photos reviewed by Michele D.

author: Michele D.
title: Michele D.
text: I'm going to be honest, I was super skeptical! However, I can't begin to tell you how the entire process was super easy and fast! Instructions were straightforward, and the pop up window for questions was also helpful. What I paid for my entire order, was less than going to a retail store to have one passport photo taken. I didn't even realize my photos were at CVS the same day I placed my order, until I opened my iPad later that evening! I have already referred someone to this site. So glad I stumbled upon this site after a Google search for passport photos.
